        Flow:

        2. Checks if booking is confirmed
        3. Checks payment status (if payment is required)
        4. Prevents duplicate attendance marking
        5. Marks attendance and updates booking status to 'attended'
        6. Returns booking and user details
        
        Use this endpoint when scanning QR codes at event entrance.
